How to Format Numbers as Currency in Excel?
CTRL + SHIFT +1 FROM THIS FORMAT CELL DIALOG BOX CHOOSE CURRENCY
How to insert border in Excel with Format Cells dialog?
HOME - BOTTOM BORDER
What are the steps to format numbers in Excel with the Percent style?
CTRL + SHIFT +1 - FORMAT CELL BOX - PERCENTAGE
What is a shortcut to merge two or more cells in excel?
HIGHLIGHT CONTENT AND PRESS ALT+M+M
How do you use text commands in Excel?
TO CONVERT NUMBERS TO TEXT
How many types of conditions are available in conditional formatting on Excel?
THERE ARE 3
